📂 How to Use

Add values according to you its just a sample file for reference

collaborators can see which values are required.

Do not commit real secrets — only placeholders.

When deploying:

Add Secrets in GitHub → for sensitive values (passwords, usernames, host ports, private images).

Add Variables in GitHub → for non‑sensitive configs (container names, ports, image names).


# ============================================================
# IMPORTANT NOTICE:
# Do NOT use special characters in POSTGRES_PASSWORD.
# Special characters can break connection strings and cause
# authentication errors. Use only alphanumeric values.
# ============================================================

# ============================
# PostgreSQL (Database)
# ============================
POSTGRES_CONTAINER_NAME=postgres-container   # GitHub Variable
POSTGRES_IMAGE=postgres:15                   # GitHub Variable
POSTGRES_HOST_PORT=5432                      # GitHub Secret
POSTGRES_CONTAINER_PORT=5432                 # GitHub Variable
POSTGRES_USER=username                       # GitHub Secret
POSTGRES_PASSWORD=supersecurepassword        # GitHub Secret  
POSTGRES_DB=mydatabase                       # GitHub Secret

# ============================
# Redis (Cache)
# ============================
REDIS_CONTAINER_NAME=redis-container         # GitHub Variable
REDIS_IMAGE=redis:7                          # GitHub Variable
REDIS_HOST_PORT=6379                         # GitHub Variable
REDIS_CONTAINER_PORT=6379                    # GitHub Variable

# ============================
# Backend (API Service)
# ============================
BACKEND_CONTAINER_NAME=backend-container     # GitHub Variable
BACKEND_IMAGE=myorg/backend:latest           # GitHub Secret
BACKEND_HOST_PORT=8000                       # GitHub Secret
BACKEND_CONTAINER_PORT=8000                  # GitHub Variable

# ============================
# Frontend (UI Service)
# ============================
FRONTEND_CONTAINER_NAME=frontend-container   # GitHub Variable
FRONTEND_IMAGE=myorg/frontend:latest         # GitHub Secret
FRONTEND_HOST_PORT=8080                      # GitHub Variable
FRONTEND_CONTAINER_PORT=80               # GitHub Variable

# ============================
# Nginx Reverse Proxy
# ============================
NGINX_CONTAINER_NAME=nginx-container         # GitHub Variable
NGINX_IMAGE=myorg/nginx:latest               # GitHub Secret
NGINX_HOST_PORT=80                           # GitHub Variable
NGINX_CONTAINER_PORT=80                      # GitHub Variable
